flowchart TD
  START([led_task_start]) --> HW[led_hardware_init nebo simulation_mode]
  HW --> MUX[led_unified_mutex · NVS jas · animation_manager_init]
  MUX --> PAT[led_clear_all_internal · led_show_chess_board]
  PAT --> LOOP{{for ;;}}

  LOOP --> WDT[WDT reset]
  WDT --> Q[led_process_commands — LED_CMD_*]
  Q --> A1[led_update_animation]
  A1 --> A2[led_update_endgame_wave]
  A2 --> A3[led_process_duration_expirations]
  A3 --> A4[led_process_button_blink_timers]
  A4 --> COMM[led_privileged_batch_commit — RMT refresh]
  COMM --> DLY[vTaskDelayUntil ~33 ms]
  DLY --> LOOP
